{"tid":1827793,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(當手足係condom？)行動post，推呀，唔好慣呀","createTime":"2020-01-17T08:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T03:55:13.000Z","uid":290787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"61b2ee83fdb8dde227f93fdf63b82f36d3042271","tid":1827793,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aBCifjO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaBCifjO.jpg&h=10d09c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【手足，和你團年】聲援在囚手足集會<br />\n日期：22/1/2020（年廿八晚）星期三<br />\n時間：8:00pm開始<br />\n地點：荔枝角收押所外（九龍蝴蝶谷道5號）<br />\n⭐不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<br />\n反修例運動至今逾7000人被捕，超過120位手足被囚錮在不同院所，當中有還柙候審，亦有已經判刑的男女手足，而荔枝角懲教所是最多手足被關柙的院所。<br />\n<br />\n一日有手足身陷囹圄，我們就沒有放棄的可能。我們沒有忘記在囚手足，給手足「人數的」支持，成為手足支撐下去的動力。我們將在年廿八晚（22/1/2020）在荔枝角收押所舉辦【手足，和你團年】聲援手足集會，與手足一起「有粥食粥」，一起吃一個清茶淡飯團年飯，讓手足們知道香港人不會讓你們孤單。<br />\n<br />\n年廿八，和你團年撐手足！！！<br />\n<br />\n⭐大會呼籲⭐<br />\n<br />\n1. 當晚集會除邀請在囚手足家屬及支援團體發言外，我們希望在集會現場與在囚手足一起食團年飯。到場巿民請自攜清茶淡飯（或監獄僅有的零食種類），象徵「有粥食粥」，與在囚手足連成一線、和勇不分共享的手足團年飯。<br />\n<br />\n2. 一切外賣的清茶淡飯（或零食），請到黃店選購。<br />\n<br />\n3. 除了光復香港，同時要做一個愛惜地球的人，請自攜餐盒及餐具購買外賣。<br />\n<br />\n親友平日可入給還柙手足的小食：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csd.gov.hk/tc_chi/socialvisit/socialvisit_articles/mrp_sso.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fsocialvisit%2Fsocialvisit_articles%2Fmrp_sso.html&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcysv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=22dff8ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csd.gov.hk/tc_chi/socialvisit/socialvisit_articles/mrp_sso.html</a><br />\n<br />\n主辦團體：<br />\n邵家臻立法會議員辦事處<br />\nFernando Chiu-hung Cheung 張超雄立法會議員辦事處<br />\n社會民主連線<br />\n<br />\nsources：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bottleshiukachun/photos/a.148060658713260/1267405403445441/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbottleshiukachun%2Fphotos%2Fa.148060658713260%2F1267405403445441%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcysv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=875938de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bottleshiukachun/photos/a.148060658713260/1267405403445441/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"772374df87acc45476528b5402f152d9adddad4d","tid":1827793,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:33:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f76c675b795da9083ac18c8b493486f2f3f7eb6b","tid":1827793,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:33:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"503345d073bd2f0b2afafd85e95bc45d59e25e88","tid":1827793,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:34:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1ab777f595c676c9a5dfa2e658b9dee7d0d3ae33","tid":1827793,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f3f0f8ba6882f3de981bafb8495b02395f703a","tid":1827793,"uid":233338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35a817cf61af66225142ea37a32e4253189dc3a4","tid":1827793,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:17:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"95861511c911a8042e322918e6307f09b630690e","tid":1827793,"uid":262091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"點解無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b30a12bf9edde756d2f57e111031ab8d1eebec0","tid":1827793,"uid":290787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n屌你地，當手足係condom?"}]}